text: A crackme is a small program designed to test a programmers reverse engineering skills. It is also known by the terms reversemes and keygenmes. They are created to have a legal way to "crack" software. ==Other websites == *crackmes.de - A great site for testing your reversing skills. Crackmes range from Very Easy to Very Hard [1-9] for many Operating systems *phmaster.info - Polish site with a lots of task. You can find many crackme's. Category:Software
title: Crackme
